  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large comal over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the red peppers and cook until they start to soften.",
    "Add the yuzu cure, tomato paste, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chickpeas and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the cover and simmer for an additional 10 minutes, or until the peppers are gooey.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
